Detailed Description

cvmx_usbn::_dma0_outb_chn4

USBN_DMA0_OUTB_CHN4 = USBN's Outbound DMA for USB0 Channel4

Contains the starting address for use when USB0 reads from L2C via Channel4. Writing of this register sets the base address.
